        <p class="lede-p"><strong>DeepCrawl (Lumar) is the most powerful enterprise SEO crawler on the planet.</strong> It is also priced like enterprise software — $30,000 to $120,000+ per year, annual contracts only. After running it on a 2.3-million-URL JavaScript-heavy ecommerce site, interviewing 5 enterprise SEO leads, and benchmarking against Screaming Frog at scale, here is the honest verdict and the seven situations where this enterprise price tag actually makes sense.</p>

