            <div class="cc-row"><span>Content team (writers + editor)</span><strong>$5,000</strong></div>
            <div class="cc-row"><span>Dev hours for technical fixes</span><strong>$4,000</strong></div>
            <div class="cc-row cc-row-total"><span>What you actually spend</span><strong>$24,249 /mo</strong></div>
          </div>
          <div class="cc-vs">
