              <strong>$167 /mo</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="cc-save">
              <span>For SMBs &amp; mid-market</span>
              <span><strong>Skip enterprise tooling entirely</strong> — get content + ranks instead</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cc-foot">
            <p>Not a Fortune 500? You probably don't need this stack. Let's audit your site.</p>
            <a href="/demo/">Get my free audit →</a>
