        <h2 id="pros-cons">Pros and cons after enterprise testing</h2>

        <div class="pros-cons">
          <div class="pros-card">
            <h4>✓ What DeepCrawl gets right</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Infinite-scale crawler — handles 10M+ URLs without choking</li>
              <li>Real Chromium JavaScript rendering (vs basic JS approximation)</li>
              <li>Log Analyzer surfaces wasted Googlebot crawl budget</li>
