            <h4>✗ Where DeepCrawl hurts</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>$30k–$120k/year — enterprise only, no SMB tier</li>
              <li>Annual contracts only — no monthly billing</li>
              <li>No free trial — demo + sales call gates the price</li>
              <li>Steep learning curve — non-engineers struggle in week one</li>
              <li>No content tools, keyword research, or rank tracking</li>
