        <p><strong>At 2M+ URLs, you have three real options:</strong> DeepCrawl, Botify, or OnCrawl. All three are enterprise priced ($30k+/year). Below 500k URLs, Screaming Frog at $259/yr is the better tool every single time — cheaper, faster, runs on your laptop.</p>

        <blockquote class="pull">
          "DeepCrawl is the price you pay to know what Google sees on a million-URL site. We discovered our faceted navigation was generating 800,000 indexed URLs we never intended. The log analyzer paid for the entire annual contract in one quarter."
          <cite>— SEO Lead, enterprise ecommerce, $4B annual revenue</cite>
