        <h2 id="who-its-for">Who DeepCrawl is best for — and who should skip</h2>

        <h3>Strong fit</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Enterprise sites with 1M+ URLs (ecommerce, marketplaces, publishers)</li>
          <li>JavaScript-heavy SPAs (Next.js, React, Vue, Angular)</li>
